  <!-- EN: {WEAPON}'s calm thoughts -->
  <BondedThoughtCalm.stages.s_calm_thoughts.label>{WEAPON}의 차분한 속삭임</BondedThoughtCalm.stages.s_calm_thoughts.label>
  <!-- EN: {WEAPON}, my bonded weapon, is whispering calming thoughts to me. -->
  <BondedThoughtCalm.stages.s_calm_thoughts.description>결속무기 {WEAPON}(이)가 차분한 생각을 속삭이고 있어.</BondedThoughtCalm.stages.s_calm_thoughts.description>
  
  <!-- EN: {WEAPON}'s kind thoughts -->
  <BondedThoughtKind.stages.s_kind_thoughts.label>{WEAPON}의 친절한 속삭임</BondedThoughtKind.stages.s_kind_thoughts.label>
  <!-- EN: {WEAPON}, my bonded weapon, is whispering kind thoughts to me. -->
  <BondedThoughtKind.stages.s_kind_thoughts.description>결속무기 {WEAPON}(이)가 친절한 생각을 속삭이고 있어.</BondedThoughtKind.stages.s_kind_thoughts.description>
  
  <!-- EN: {WEAPON}'s muttering -->
  <BondedThoughtMuttering.stages.s_muttering.label>{WEAPON}의 중얼거림</BondedThoughtMuttering.stages.s_muttering.label>
  <!-- EN: {WEAPON}, my bonded weapon, is muttering in my head. It's hard to ignore sometimes. -->
  <BondedThoughtMuttering.stages.s_muttering.description>결속무기 {WEAPON}(이)가 머릿속에서 중얼거리고 있어. 가끔은 무시하기 너무 힘들어.</BondedThoughtMuttering.stages.s_muttering.description>
  
  <!-- EN: {WEAPON}'s wailing -->
  <BondedThoughtWailing.stages.s_wailing.label>{WEAPON}의 울부짖음</BondedThoughtWailing.stages.s_wailing.label>
  <!-- EN: {WEAPON}, my bonded weapon, is wailing madly in my head. I wish I could ignore it. -->
  <BondedThoughtWailing.stages.s_wailing.description>결속무기 {WEAPON}(이)가 머릿속에서 미친듯이 울부짖고 있어. 너무 신경쓰여.</BondedThoughtWailing.stages.s_wailing.description>
  
  <!-- EN: {WEAPON}'s jealousy -->
  <JealousRage.stages.s_jealousy.label>{WEAPON}의 질투</JealousRage.stages.s_jealousy.label>
  <!-- EN: My bonded weapon {WEAPON} is jealous I am using another weapon. I can feel the rage it is screaming into my head. -->
  <JealousRage.stages.s_jealousy.description>다른 무기를 착용한 것 때문에 {WEAPON}(이)가 질투하고 있어. 머릿 속이 분노한 비명 소리로 가득해.</JealousRage.stages.s_jealousy.description>
  
  <!-- EN: {WEAPON}'s kill thirst -->
  <KillThirst_Weapon.stages.s_kill_thirst.label>{WEAPON}의 살해 갈망</KillThirst_Weapon.stages.s_kill_thirst.label>
  <!-- EN: My bonded weapon {WEAPON} is angry it has gone so long without killing. I can feel its rage. -->
  <KillThirst_Weapon.stages.s_kill_thirst.description>{WEAPON}(이)가 피 맛을 원해. 끝없는 분노가 느껴져.</KillThirst_Weapon.stages.s_kill_thirst.description>
  
  <!-- EN: {WEAPON}'s kill sorrow -->
  <OnKill_BadThought.stages.s_kill_sorrow.label>{WEAPON}의 비애감</OnKill_BadThought.stages.s_kill_sorrow.label>
  <!-- EN: {WEAPON}'s sorrow over its kill is affecting my mind as well. -->
  <OnKill_BadThought.stages.s_kill_sorrow.description>{WEAPON}(은)는 사람을 죽인 것에 슬퍼하고 있어. 마음 속까지 전해져.</OnKill_BadThought.stages.s_kill_sorrow.description>
  
  <!-- EN: {WEAPON}'s kill happiness -->
  <OnKill_GoodThought.stages.s_kill_happiness.label>{WEAPON}의 행복감</OnKill_GoodThought.stages.s_kill_happiness.label>
  <!-- EN: {WEAPON} was overjoyed with its kill, and I feel some of that too. -->
  <OnKill_GoodThought.stages.s_kill_happiness.description>{WEAPON}(은)는 사람을 죽이고 기뻐하고 있어, 나도 조금은 그 기분을 알 것 같아.</OnKill_GoodThought.stages.s_kill_happiness.description>
  
